00:09:19.539 --> 00:09:26.340
We hope you're not counting calories during this annual meeting season.

00:09:26.340 --> 00:09:33.259
But whatever your choice, the energy and food is a gift of Almighty God to help sustain

00:09:33.259 --> 00:09:35.059
us, to recharge us.

00:09:35.059 --> 00:09:42.340
And now a question that we ask, though, what happens when we become tired of dealing with

00:09:42.340 --> 00:09:45.299
life's trials?

00:09:45.299 --> 00:09:49.340
Maybe with problems that don't have a solution in this system of things.

00:09:49.340 --> 00:09:56.820
Well, when we maintain a good spiritual routine, then Jehovah gives us power, power to the

00:09:56.820 --> 00:09:58.179
tired one.

00:09:58.179 --> 00:10:03.820
His Holy Spirit strengthens us, enables us to go forward in the battle yet another day.

00:10:03.820 --> 00:10:07.700
The power beyond what is normal strengthens us.

00:10:07.700 --> 00:10:10.460
Yes, Jehovah gives power to the tired one.

00:10:10.460 --> 00:10:16.279
We might say that Jehovah loves us with all his strength.

00:10:16.279 --> 00:10:20.519
Doesn't that draw you to him as a person?

00:10:20.519 --> 00:10:23.320
Let's consider another reason we have to love Jehovah.

00:10:23.320 --> 00:10:32.340
This time in Isaiah chapter 41, verses 10 and 13, there our God says,

00:10:32.340 --> 00:10:38.340
Do not be afraid, for I am with you.

00:10:38.340 --> 00:10:41.580
Do not be anxious for I am your God.

00:10:41.580 --> 00:10:44.419
I will fortify you, yes, I will help you.

00:10:44.419 --> 00:10:50.179
I will really hold on to you with my right hand of righteousness.

00:10:50.179 --> 00:10:57.100
Verse 13, for I Jehovah your God am grasping your right hand.

00:10:57.100 --> 00:11:04.750
The one saying to you, Do not be afraid, I will help you.

00:11:04.750 --> 00:11:13.480
Jehovah is our helper, Jehovah grasps our right hand with his right hand of righteousness.

00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:19.960
