00:12:11.679 --> 00:12:17.320
He took hold of me and pulled me from deep waters.

00:12:17.320 --> 00:12:20.600
Verse 19, He brought me out into a place of safety.

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:28.070
He rescued me because he was pleased with me.

00:12:28.070 --> 00:12:32.350
Can you imagine Jehovah reaching down with his right hand of righteousness and rescuing

00:12:32.350 --> 00:12:35.700
you from a trial?

00:12:35.700 --> 00:12:37.860
Why?

00:12:37.860 --> 00:12:46.129
Because Jehovah loves us with all his soul, his whole being.

00:12:46.129 --> 00:12:48.529
How does that make you feel?

00:12:48.529 --> 00:12:54.519
Does it draw you closer to your Heavenly Father?

00:12:54.519 --> 00:12:58.320
Let's consider a fourth reason we have to love Jehovah.

00:12:58.320 --> 00:13:03.620
Isaiah chapter 42 verses 8 and 9.

00:13:03.620 --> 00:13:06.220
It says, I am Jehovah.

00:13:06.220 --> 00:13:08.059
That is my name.

00:13:08.059 --> 00:13:12.539
I give my glory to no one else, nor my praise to graven images.

00:13:12.539 --> 00:13:15.259
See, the first things have come to pass.

00:13:15.259 --> 00:13:17.259
