00:13:17.259 --> 00:13:22.700
Before they spring up, I tell you about them.

00:13:22.700 --> 00:13:25.139
Why is this a reason to love Jehovah?

00:13:25.139 --> 00:13:27.340
He's a God of prophecy.

00:13:27.340 --> 00:13:28.820
What does that mean in simple terms?

00:13:28.820 --> 00:13:30.419
Well, Jehovah keeps his promises.

00:13:30.419 --> 00:13:37.220
It's linked to his name, Jehovah, which we understand to mean he causes to become.

00:13:37.220 --> 00:13:44.659
Not one word of all his good promise that he made through Moses, his servant, has failed.

00:13:44.659 --> 00:13:47.480
You said it.

00:13:47.480 --> 00:13:53.080
