00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:07.000
God's kingdom rules.

00:14:07.000 --> 00:14:09.159
Pure worship has been restored.

00:14:09.159 --> 00:14:17.519
We can emphatically say not one word of all Jehovah's good promises has failed.

00:14:17.519 --> 00:14:21.080
But how does that make us love him more?

00:14:21.080 --> 00:14:24.840
