00:14:33.360 --> 00:14:41.000
about the effect that the disappearance of sickness, pain, and death will have for us and

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:49.259
for our loved ones, the resurrection.

00:14:49.340 --> 00:14:54.000
Do you long to welcome back loved ones?

00:14:54.000 --> 00:14:57.610
It's as good as done.

00:14:57.610 --> 00:15:00.529
God's personal name is a guarantee.

00:15:00.529 --> 00:15:06.289
Jehovah makes the dead alive and calls the things that are not as though they are.

00:15:06.289 --> 00:15:07.450
Why?

00:15:07.450 --> 00:15:13.950
Because his promises are absolutely certain of fulfillment.

00:15:13.950 --> 00:15:17.750
Jeremiah chapter 29 verse 11.

00:15:17.750 --> 00:15:23.190
There Jehovah says, I will know the thoughts that I am thinking toward you.

00:15:23.190 --> 00:15:27.629
Lots of peace and not of calamity to give you a future and a hope.

00:15:27.629 --> 00:15:31.909
We might say Jehovah loves us with all his mind.

00:15:31.909 --> 00:15:37.309
Jehovah will make his very own thoughts toward you a reality.

00:15:37.309 --> 00:15:39.309
How does that make you feel?

00:15:39.309 --> 00:15:44.669
Well, from Isaiah's prophecy, we've considered just four reasons to love Jehovah.

00:15:44.669 --> 00:15:46.909
First, he's our shepherd.

00:15:46.909 --> 00:15:48.710
Second, he's our creator.

00:15:48.710 --> 00:15:50.590
Third, he's our helper.

00:15:50.590 --> 00:15:52.710
And finally, he's a God of prophecy.

