But many don't want to listen.

00:19:11.660 --> 00:19:14.660
What if we face opposition even from governments?

00:19:14.660 --> 00:19:24.059
Isaiah 44 verse 8 is what we need to keep in mind, because as we've considered already,

00:19:24.059 --> 00:19:28.660
during this program, the time will come when we're going to face opposition.

00:19:28.660 --> 00:19:33.740
Isaiah 44 verse 8, some of our brothers in many places are already facing opposition.

00:19:33.740 --> 00:19:38.579
Notice what it says, do not be in dread, do not become paralyzed with fear.

00:19:38.579 --> 00:19:43.339
Have I not told each of you beforehand and declared it, you are my witnesses.

00:19:43.339 --> 00:19:45.059
Is there any God but me?

00:19:45.059 --> 00:19:46.460
No, there is no other rock.

00:19:46.460 --> 00:19:49.539
I know of none.

00:19:49.539 --> 00:19:56.700
Jehovah says, do not be in dread, do not become paralyzed with fear.

00:19:56.700 --> 00:20:01.140
We back Caesar's things to Caesar, but God's things to God.

00:20:01.140 --> 00:20:06.539
Caesar is on shaky ground when he interferes with what God requires.

00:20:06.539 --> 00:20:11.220
So rather than being paralyzed with fear, love for Jehovah conquers fear and moves us to

00:20:11.220 --> 00:20:14.420
continue praising him.

00:20:14.420 --> 00:20:18.539
And we've seized such determination in our international family of witnesses, a faithful

00:20:18.539 --> 00:20:21.259
sister named Tatiana.

00:20:21.259 --> 00:20:25.619
Her criminal case for praising Jehovah is pending, and her husband is currently in

00:20:25.619 --> 00:20:28.099
pretrial detention.

00:20:28.099 --> 00:20:32.759
But she says, during the most difficult moments, I continue to sense that Jehovah is with

00:20:32.759 --> 00:20:39.259
me and I feel confident that with his help, I can endure whatever trials may yet come.

00:20:39.259 --> 00:20:43.900
My heart is filled with peace and calmness.

00:20:43.900 --> 00:20:47.539
I am more determined than ever to tell others about Jehovah.

00:20:47.539 --> 00:20:51.940
I am proud to be one of Jehovah's witnesses.

00:20:51.940 --> 00:20:59.940
Yes, Tatiana's love for Jehovah moves her to continue praising him.

00:20:59.940 --> 00:21:05.779
Well, the Bible doesn't tell us how many hours we have to share in the ministry each month.

00:21:05.779 --> 00:21:11.099
But it does tell us that love for God must be our motivation.

00:21:11.099 --> 00:21:15.900
The greater our love, the fuller our share will be in accord with our personal circumstances.

00:21:15.900 --> 00:21:20.500
We prove that we are Jehovah's witnesses by our conduct and by our zeal in praising

00:21:20.500 --> 00:21:22.740
him formally and informally.

00:21:22.740 --> 00:21:28.240
May our deep love for Jehovah move us to tell as many people as possible about our great

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:29.500
God, Jehovah.
